OL,3,CShoplifters caught on camera as police
OL,4,Claunch app to catch culprits
OL,6,FBusiness have welcomed a scheme
OL,7,Ftargeting prolific shoplifters, as
OL,8,Foffences reach an all time high across
OL,9,FDevon and Cornwall.
OL,11,FAccording to the latest ONS data,
OL,12,Fthere has been a 40% increase in
OL,13,Fshoplifting offences this year,
OL,14,Fcompared to 2024 - more than 11,000
OL,15,Foffences in total. This is the highest
OL,16,Fnumber since comparable records began
OL,17,Fin 2002.
