OL,3,CShoplifters caught on camera as police
OL,4,Claunch app to catch culprits
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall's Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner has partnered with UK
OL,8,FPartners Against Crime (UKPAC), to
OL,9,Flaunch a year-long pilot scheme
OL,10,Ftackling the issue.
OL,12,FAny kind of business can sign up, from
OL,13,Fretail to hospitality, and allows
OL,14,Fstaff to quickly and easily report a
OL,15,Fcrime through the online portal.
OL,17,FThis means intelligence can be shared
OL,18,Fwith the police, and ultimately lead
OL,19,Fto more prosecutions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
