OL,3,CShoplifters caught on camera as police
OL,4,Claunch app to catch culprits
OL,6,FSo far, the current areas being
OL,7,Ftargeted are Torbay, Saltash, Liskeard
OL,8,Fand Barnstaple, but there are plans
OL,9,Ffor a wider rollout across the force
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FMikey Johnson, from UKPAC, said: "This
OL,13,Fplatform allows businesses to upload
OL,14,Ftheir CCTV straight away, not waiting
OL,15,Ffor anybody to come and ask for it. It
OL,16,Fallows them to create that witness
OL,17,Fstatement - many cases are dropped
OL,18,Fbecause there is no witness statement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
