OL,3,CShoplifters caught on camera as police
OL,4,Claunch app to catch culprits
OL,6,F"It's a process which some police
OL,7,Fforces say take three weeks, we've now
OL,8,Fput that down to 20 mins. The report
OL,9,Fis ready to go, so when it hits that
OL,10,Fpolice officer's desk, it's ready for
OL,11,Finvestigation."
OL,13,FRachel Venn, manager of a toy shop in
OL,14,FTorquay, said her store is targeted
OL,15,Fevery other day: "It's been awful to
OL,16,Fbe honest, I worry about the safety of
OL,17,Fmy staff and we work with children, so
OL,18,FI worry about that too.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
