OL,3,CShoplifters caught on camera as police
OL,4,Claunch app to catch culprits
OL,6,F"People aren't coming up here because
OL,7,Fof the thefts and all the crime. I
OL,8,Fsometimes do worry, are we going to
OL,9,Fmake it."
OL,11,FAs soon as Rachel heard about the
OL,12,Fpilot scheme, she signed up: "I feel
OL,13,Flike I'm not going to worry about the
OL,14,Fsafety of my staff as much, and my
OL,15,Fcustomers.
OL,17,F"It's a toy shop, we're meant to have
OL,18,Ffun in here and we shouldn't have to
OL,19,Fworry about running after people to
OL,20,Fget our stuff back," Rachel explained.
