OL,3,CShoplifters caught on camera as police
OL,4,Claunch app to catch culprits
OL,6,FThe scheme has already had some
OL,7,Fsuccesses, according to Devon and
OL,8,FCornwall's Police and Crime
OL,9,FCommissioner, Alison Hernandez.
OL,11,FScott Whatley, 35 of Smythen Street in
OL,12,FExeter, targeted a single store in
OL,13,FTorquay 10 times, with the thefts
OL,14,Ftotalling almost #400.
OL,16,FThrough intelligence sharing, a case
OL,17,Fwas built linking all 10 offences.
OL,18,FWhatley will be sentenced on 16
OL,19,FSeptember.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
