OL,3,CShoplifters caught on camera as police
OL,4,Claunch app to catch culprits
OL,6,FInspector Robert Harvey, force lead in
OL,7,FTorquay, said this scheme is a crucial
OL,8,Fway of improving public confidence in
OL,9,Fthe police - and to show that
OL,10,Fshoplifting is taken seriously.
OL,12,F"There is a pressure, however it is a
OL,13,Fcommunity issue that we want to
OL,14,Fresolve and do better at.
OL,16,F"What they see happening in the town
OL,17,Fcentre is a direct link to confidence
OL,18,Fwithin policing, and that's something
OL,19,Fwe want to improve on.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
